0.8346
Epoch 4/6
176/176 [==============================] - 235s - loss: 0.0297 - acc: 0.9913 - val_loss: 0.8754 - val_acc: 0.8206
Epoch 5/6
176/176 [==============================] - 235s - loss: 0.0245 - acc: 0.9933 - val_loss: 0.6739 - val_acc: 0.8658
Epoch 6/6
176/176 [==============================] - 234s - loss: 0.0189 - acc: 0.9949 - val_loss: 0.9973 - val_acc: 0.8253
